      <title>特里·史密斯因担心减肥药而抛售帝亚吉欧股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/terry-smith-sells-diageo-stock-on-concern-over-weight-loss-drugs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国基金经理特里史密斯 (Terry Smith) 出售了其在帝亚吉欧 (Diageo Plc) 的股份，理由是担心该饮料公司的管理及其对减肥药物需求飙升的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/terry-smith-sells-diageo-stock-on-concern-over-weight-loss-drugs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 13:39:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
